    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You shout a warning to your allies, focusing their attention on the threats around them.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Cha 15.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a move action, you can shout a warning to your allies, ending the @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-footed} condition for any ally within 60 feet. You cannot use this feat when you’re @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-footed}. Once you’ve used this ability, you cannot do so again until you’ve regained Stamina Points after a 10-minute rest. This is a @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.PqV3OCbUTyk2upPD]{Sense-dependent} ability.</span></p>",
